===''Moby Dick''===
Teenage boys '''Tom''' and '''Tubb''' are rescued by the great white [[whale]] '''Moby Dick''' after a shipwreck. Together with their pet [[Pinniped|seal]], '''Scooby''', they face the dangers of the undersea world. Tom is voiced by [[Bobby Resnick]], Tubb is voiced by [[Barry Balkin]], and Moby and Scooby are voiced by [[Don Messick]].

